# Quality gate (TTD)

Agent work is **not done** until **`just check`** passes in the repo root.

## Required before handoff

```bash
just check
```

This runs:

- `uv run ruff check .`
- `uv run ruff format --check .`
- `uv run ty check`

Fix any reported issues (or narrow the change scope) and re-run until exit code 0.

## When to run more

| Command | When |
|---------|------|
| `just check` | Default gate after code changes |
| `uv run pytest` | Behavior or logic changed |
| `prek run --all-files` | Pre-PR / CI parity (hooks include pytest, docs build, etc.) |

Git hooks installed via `just setup` / `uv run prek install` also run ruff and ty on commit (see `prek.toml`).

Do not claim a task is complete, ready for review, or passing CI if `just check` has not been run successfully on the current tree.
